sql:
SELECT articles.id AS PHXal_id, articles.idUser AS PHXal_idUser, articles.title AS PHXal_title, articles.hook AS PHXal_hook, articles.content AS PHXal_content, articles.url AS PHXal_url, articles.date AS PHXal_date, articles.idCateg AS PHXal_idCateg 
FROM `articles` 
ORDER BY date DESC
LIMIT 0,8
